{
  "page": "Lyonel Corbray",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\"><img alt=\"House Corbray.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/50px-House_Corbray.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/75px-House_Corbray.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/100px-House_Corbray.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Lyonel Corbray</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\"><img alt=\"House Corbray.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/50px-House_Corbray.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/75px-House_Corbray.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/100px-House_Corbray.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Heart%27s_Home\" title=\"Lord of Heart&#39;s Home\">Lord of Heart's Home</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\">House Corbray</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260&#160;AC</a> (roughly)<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Heart%27s_Home\" title=\"Heart&#39;s Home\">Heart's Home</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaflyonel_corbray.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaflyonel_corbray.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Corbray_(father_of_Lyonel)\" title=\"Lord Corbray (father of Lyonel)\">Corbray</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouses</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>1<sup>st</sup>: Unknown<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li><li>2<sup>nd</sup>: <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Corbray\" title=\"Lady Corbray\">A merchant's daughter</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Sickly babe<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li><li>Unborn child<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lyonel Corbray</b> is the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Heart%27s_Home\" title=\"Heart&#39;s Home\">Heart's Home</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\">House Corbray</a>, an ancient but impoverished family.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> He has two younger brothers, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lyn_Corbray\" title=\"Lyn Corbray\">Lyn</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lucas_Corbray\" title=\"Lucas Corbray\">Lucas</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyonel_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lyonel is over forty years old.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lyn_Corbray\" title=\"Lyn Corbray\">Lyn Corbray</a> dislikes his elder brother.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyonel_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Corbray_(father_of_Lyonel)\" title=\"Lord Corbray (father of Lyonel)\">Lord Corbray</a> was wounded during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Battle of the Trident\">Battle of the Trident</a>, Lyonel carried his father back to the <a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\">maesters</a> in the rear, while his younger brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lyn_Corbray\" title=\"Lyn Corbray\">Lyn Corbray</a>, grabbed their father's sword, <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Forlorn\" title=\"Lady Forlorn\">Lady Forlorn</a>, and led a charge against the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a>. When Lord Corbray died, Lyonel inherited the titles and lands while Lyn received Lady Forlorn. Lyonel felt he was cheated of his birthright.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lyonel's wife bore a sickly child who died in infancy, so Lyonel's heir is his brother, Lyn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyonel_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyonel_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Having <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Petyr_Baelish_and_Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Wedding of Petyr Baelish and Lysa Arryn\">married Lysa Arryn</a> and been named <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Protector_of_the_Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lord Protector of the Vale\">Lord Protector of the Vale</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> travels to meet with the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\">Corbrays</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyonel_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord Lyonel does not join with the <a href=\"/index.php/Lords_Declarant\" title=\"Lords Declarant\">Lords Declarant</a> who try to depose Petyr as Lord Protector.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lyonel marries the sixteen-year-old <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Corbray\" title=\"Lady Corbray\">daughter</a> of a rich <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a> merchant, a marriage brokered by Petyr after the death of Lyonel's first wife.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Lyonel receives a significant <a href=\"/index.php/Dowry\" title=\"Dowry\">dowry</a> for marrying a <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">commoner</a>. It is <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Lyonel_Corbray_and_Lady_Corbray\" title=\"Wedding of Lyonel Corbray and Lady Corbray\">a well-attended wedding</a>, with Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Benedar_Belmore\" title=\"Benedar Belmore\">Benedar Belmore</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Grafton\" title=\"Gerold Grafton\">Gerold Grafton</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Lynderly\" title=\"Jon Lynderly\">Jon Lynderly</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Symond_Templeton\" title=\"Symond Templeton\">Symond Templeton</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Waxley\" title=\"House Waxley\">Waxley</a>, and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Anya_Waynwood\" title=\"Anya Waynwood\">Anya Waynwood</a> present.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Petyr sends word that Lyonel is pleased with his new wife and her dowry.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyonel_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Lord Lyonel does not attend the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_of_Winged_Knights\" title=\"Brotherhood of Winged Knights\">Brotherhood of Winged Knights</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a>, remaining at <a href=\"/index.php/Heart%27s_Home\" title=\"Heart&#39;s Home\">Heart's Home</a> with his new wife, who is now pregnant with his long-desired heir.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyonel_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Lord Lyonel Corbray is well disposed toward my rule, but <a href=\"/index.php/Lyn_Corbray\" title=\"Lyn Corbray\">his brother</a> goes his own way.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>We have had a letter from <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">your father</a>. He is on his way <a href=\"/index.php/Giant%27s_Lance\" title=\"Giant&#39;s Lance\">home</a>, he says, and hopes to see his darling daughter soon. He writes that Lyonel Corbray seems well pleased with <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Corbray\" title=\"Lady Corbray\">his bride</a>, and even more so with her dowry. I do hope Lord Lyonel remembers which one he needs to bed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Myranda_Royce\" title=\"Myranda Royce\">Myranda Royce</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Alayne Stone</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Alayne</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">My lord father</a> tells me your brother's <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Corbray\" title=\"Lady Corbray\">new wife</a> is with child.<br />\n<b>Lyn</b>: Lyonel sends his regrets. He remains at <a href=\"/index.php/Heart%27s_Home\" title=\"Heart&#39;s Home\">Heart's Home</a> with his peddler's daughter, watching her belly swell as if he were the first man who ever got a wench pregnant.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_4-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Alayne Stone</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lyn_Corbray\" title=\"Lyn Corbray\">Lyn Corbray</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyonel_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><